00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:52,252
Whether it's a King or only
some low‐level clansmen,

70
00:04:52,285 --> 00:04:53,754
who the hell cares?!

71
00:04:53,754 --> 00:04:57,390
We'll crush anyone who comes
at us, so show some spirit!

72
00:04:57,423 --> 00:04:58,559
Come on!

73
00:04:59,392 --> 00:05:02,235
Oh? like this
boy's enthusiasm.

74
00:05:02,503 --> 00:05:05,105
But I meant me when
I said unfortunate!

75
00:05:06,807 --> 00:05:08,274
Hey! What the‐?!

76
00:05:08,474 --> 00:05:11,411
Since my part in this
is all over, ta‐ta!

77
00:05:12,846 --> 00:05:13,680
Shiro!

78
00:05:15,248 --> 00:05:17,518
Yeah. It appears that
he has decided it's time

79
00:05:17,584 --> 00:05:18,785
to make his move.

80
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:22,455
Although it's sooner
than I had expected...

81
00:05:22,455 --> 00:05:24,190
What'll we do, Shiro?

82
00:05:24,424 --> 00:05:27,127
Hey, who gave you guys
permission to talk, anyway?!

83
00:05:29,763 --> 00:05:30,631
[gasp]

84
00:05:34,935 --> 00:05:37,804
Ah! Damn it! Stop all
your fooling around!

85
00:05:37,838 --> 00:05:39,673
Come on! Fight me for real!

86
00:05:40,173 --> 00:05:43,176
Sukuna Gojo, this battle
of ours is not a single

87
00:05:43,209 --> 00:05:45,846
combat that will determine
the outcome of war.

88
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:48,481
Huh?! But nothing is
more important than

89
00:05:48,515 --> 00:05:51,184
winning whatever
game you're playing!

90
00:05:51,217 --> 00:05:52,786
You gotta risk everything!

91
00:05:52,819 --> 00:05:54,320
I'm betting my life!

92
00:05:54,888 --> 00:05:57,724
So you're willing to throw
your life away, huh?

93
