Then you leave
me no choice!

94
00:06:00,667 --> 00:06:02,235
He'll use a big move here.

95
00:06:02,302 --> 00:06:04,671
So counter the instant
that he first swings.

96
00:06:04,671 --> 00:06:05,572
Understood.

97
00:06:06,507 --> 00:06:08,709
I'm gonna take all of
you out, right now!

98
00:06:11,512 --> 00:06:14,347
The sun is setting. Those
who chose to leave their

99
00:06:14,347 --> 00:06:16,517
homes, and those who return.

100
00:06:16,917 --> 00:06:18,484
Yukari Mishakuji!

101
00:06:19,219 --> 00:06:21,855
Yukari! I'm right in the
middle of a game here!

102
00:06:22,523 --> 00:06:23,690
Middle of a game!

103
00:06:24,257 --> 00:06:25,592
[chuckle] Well, Kuroh...

104
00:06:26,026 --> 00:06:28,361
I see being reunited
with the Silver King has

105
00:06:28,361 --> 00:06:31,665
made you even more
handsome than ever.

106
00:06:31,698 --> 00:06:33,867
Understandable, since
you only use your

107
00:06:33,867 --> 00:06:35,569
sword to protect your King.

108
00:06:36,269 --> 00:06:38,338
It's what defines
your selfless nature.

109
00:06:39,372 --> 00:06:41,274
So have you come here
to assist your comrade

110
00:06:41,341 --> 00:06:43,777
then, Yukari Mishakuji?

111
00:06:43,844 --> 00:06:44,945
That's just dirty!

112
00:06:45,445 --> 00:06:47,280
Hey, I don't need
your help, you know!

113
00:06:47,914 --> 00:06:49,883
Assist? Or help?

114
00:06:50,551 --> 00:06:54,220
I would never do anything as
tasteless as those things.

115
00:06:54,254 --> 00:06:57,958
I just came by so that I
might pick up our boy, here.

116
00:06:58,024 --> 00:07:00,393
Come on, Sukuna. Time to go.

117
00:07:00,393 --> 00:07:03,036
Caw! Time to go! Time to go!

118
00:07:03,069 --> 00:07:05,906
No way, man! I'm
staying to fight!

119
00:07:06,807 --> 00:07:09,409
Stop being so
selfish, Sukuna.

120
00:07:09,442 --> 00:07:11,812
A child throwing
infantile tantrums is

121
00:07:11,878 --> 00:07:13,614
very unattractive.

122
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:15,582
And besides...

123
00:07:16,282 --> 00:07:18,752
I've already decided
that Kuroh will be mine.

124
00:07:19,452 --> 00:07:22,556
When the time comes, I get
to have him all to myself.

125
00:07:23,056 --> 00:07:25,425
Whatever, and you have
the nerve to say that

126
00:07:25,458 --> 00:07:26,893
I'm the selfish one here?!

127
00:07:32,799 --> 00:07:36,069
Alas, Kuroh, it seems we
just weren't destined to

128
00:07:36,102 --> 00:07:37,904
face each other tonight.

129
00:07:38,739 --> 00:07:42,509
But I'm sure that we'll
meet again very soon.

130
00:07:42,576 --> 00:07:45,345
And on that fateful
day we'll settle things

131
00:07:45,411 --> 00:07:46,913
once and for all.

132
00:07:50,517 --> 00:07:52,953
What's the deal with that
weirdo? After all the fuss

133
00:07:52,953 --> 00:07:54,621
that he caused getting
up here, he just

134
00:07:54,621 --> 00:07:56,523
decides to run off!

135
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:58,925
I mean, talk about
anticlimactic!

136
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:01,101
And who exactly am I
supposed to take out all

137
00:08:01,134 --> 00:08:02,936
my frustration on now?!

138
00:08:04,104 --> 00:08:08,008
Right, so, the kid that you
guys were just dealing with.

139
00:08:08,041 --> 00:08:10,611
Yes, that's right.
I mean Sukuna Gojo.

140
00:08:10,877 --> 00:08:13,113
Really? You're saying that
he just retreated along

141
00:08:13,146 --> 00:08:14,781
with Yukari Mishakuji?

142
00:08:15,549 --> 00:08:16,683
Okay, got it.

143
00:08:17,017 --> 00:08:19,052
It's sooner than
anticipated, but we'll go

144
00:08:19,119 --> 00:08:21,555
ahead and prepare to
move on to Phase 3.

145
00:08:21,622 --> 00:08:22,823
Yes, Mr. Shiro.

146
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:25,491
We'll all be waiting
up at the top.

147
00:08:25,826 --> 00:08:27,994
Please, sir, be very careful.

148
00:08:30,831 --> 00:08:34,400
Fushimi, we're starting
Phase 3. Everything ready?

149
00:08:34,467 --> 00:08:35,802
I was ready hours ago.

150
00:08:36,537 --> 00:08:39,139
Mihashira Tower will now
go into total lockdown,

151
00:08:39,172 --> 00:08:41,908
including all communication
and power systems.

152
00:08:41,975 --> 00:08:43,744
That will isolate
the Green King.

153
00:08:44,678 --> 00:08:47,347
And from this moment onward
our communication will be

154
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:49,916
limited to just the Red
King's psychic powers,

155
00:08:49,983 --> 00:08:52,519
so please be cautious.

156
00:08:52,553 --> 00:08:53,520
Understood.

157
00:08:54,354 --> 00:08:56,422
Right! Launch emergency
Tower lockdown.

158
00:08:56,690 --> 00:08:58,892
Yes, sir! Emergency
Tower lockdown!

159
00:09:04,605 --> 00:09:06,707
You can't use the routes
that your henchmen opened

160
00:09:06,707 --> 00:09:08,909
up, Green King.
I won't let you.

161
00:09:14,047 --> 00:09:16,049
There are no lights
along the corridors.

162
00:09:17,083 --> 00:09:19,452
And no one will be
able to hear your voice.

163
00:09:20,521 --> 00:09:23,023
Furthermore, several
layers of thick walls

164
00:09:23,056 --> 00:09:24,558
will block your way.

165
00:09:25,191 --> 00:09:28,128
All of Mihashira Tower
has now become a prison,

166
00:09:28,194 --> 00:09:30,130
custom‐made just for you.

167
00:09:31,431 --> 00:09:33,734
Obviously, a trap like this
one could never completely

168
00:09:33,734 --> 00:09:36,703
stop a powerful King
such as yourself.

169
00:09:37,604 --> 00:09:40,574
However, each trap will
certainly eat away at your

170
00:09:40,607 --> 00:09:42,576
limited time and strength.

171
00:09:44,144 --> 00:09:46,079
You'll need to break
through a hundred walls

172
00:09:46,079 --> 00:09:47,748
and get past two Kings.

173
00:09:48,582 --> 00:09:51,151
All right then, let's see
if you'll make it this far.

174
00:09:52,553 --> 00:09:55,055
Can you, Green
King, Nagare Hisui?

175
00:09:56,823 --> 00:09:57,791
[chuckle]

176
00:10:05,405 --> 00:10:08,509
Is this the damage Nagare
Hisui left behind?

177
00:10:09,075 --> 00:10:11,578
His destructive power
is simply amazing.

178
00:10:11,778 --> 00:10:15,048
Yeah, he's using up his
power at an alarming rate.

179
00:10:15,682 --> 00:10:17,718
His speed is far greater
than I expected.

180
00:10:18,451 --> 00:10:21,955
But, there's no way he
can maintain his stamina.

181
00:10:22,455 --> 00:10:25,058
Shiro, isn't that exactly
the outcome you hoped your

182
00:10:25,091 --> 00:10:26,727
strategy would produce?

183
00:10:26,927 --> 00:10:29,863
Yes, but it's happening much
faster than I anticipated.

184
00:10:30,564 --> 00:10:31,898
Its like he's not
even trying to save

185
00:10:31,898 --> 00:10:33,133
his strength at all.

186
00:10:33,567 --> 00:10:35,569
Just what could
he be up to?

187
00:10:35,569 --> 00:10:37,571
Something doesn't
feel right.

188
00:10:38,104 --> 00:10:39,139
Shiro!

189
00:10:39,205 --> 00:10:40,641
Shiro!

190
00:10:40,707 --> 00:10:41,908
Hurry up!

191
00:10:41,908 --> 00:10:43,644
So are you saying?

192
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,045
I think Anna's in danger!

193
00:10:45,478 --> 00:10:49,716
Shiro, hurry up!
Meow! Meow!

194
00:10:49,883 --> 00:10:53,219
Remember, Anna will be the
key player in this mission.

195
00:10:53,253 --> 00:10:56,089
There isn't very much we'll
be able to do during a fight

196
00:10:56,122 --> 00:10:59,726
between Kings. We'll
only get in Anna's way.

197
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:02,669
Soon, Yashiro Isana,
the Silver King,

198
00:11:02,736 --> 00:11:03,937
will join us here.

199
00:11:05,105 --> 00:11:07,007
Mr. Shiro will defend and
Anna will attack. The rest

200
00:11:07,073 --> 00:11:09,776
of us are all there for
diversion and support.

201
00:11:09,810 --> 00:11:11,778
Right! Did you
guys get that?

202
00:11:11,812 --> 00:11:12,779
Yeah!

203
00:11:13,847 --> 00:11:16,016
But Yata, What about you?
Did you get it, as well?

204
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,451
I'm not supposed to
get carried away and

205
00:11:18,484 --> 00:11:20,120
jump into battle, is that it?

206
00:11:20,153 --> 00:11:22,856
[chuckle]

207
00:11:22,923 --> 00:11:25,859
Even at a time such
as this one you

208
00:11:25,926 --> 00:11:28,595
HOMRA are full of energy.

209
00:11:28,629 --> 00:11:32,699
Please, I beg your
pardon, Red King.

210
00:11:34,635 --> 00:11:36,102
We are all connected.

211
00:11:36,269 --> 00:11:37,137
Huh?

212
00:11:37,170 --> 00:11:38,972
I said we're all connected.

213
00:11:39,105 --> 00:11:41,642
Deep down inside of
us we all share a bond.

214
00:11:42,275 --> 00:11:43,176
That's why...

215
00:11:43,844 --> 00:11:45,979
Our fire will never go out.

216
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:48,281
But what I don't get
about all of this

217
00:11:48,314 --> 00:11:50,617
is the Blue King.

218
00:11:51,317 --> 00:11:55,055
I mean, he's making Anna,
HOMRA's King, put her life

219
00:11:55,121 --> 00:11:57,824
on the line while he
gets to kick back and

220
00:11:57,858 --> 00:11:59,893
chill out up there!

221
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,668
Just who the hell
does that guy think he

222
00:12:01,702 --> 00:12:03,737
is to do that, anyway?!

223
00:12:03,804 --> 00:12:06,840
Yata, we went over all this
at the strategy meeting.

224
00:12:06,873 --> 00:12:09,743
We can't afford to let the
Green King gain entrance to

225
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:11,244
the Chamber of the Slate.

226
00:12:11,311 --> 00:12:13,880
If all of us are in here and
he somehow manages to break

227
00:12:13,914 --> 00:12:16,149
through, it would be bad.

228
00:12:16,182 --> 00:12:18,885
That's why Anna and Mr.
Shiro's job is to force the

229
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:20,854
enemy to use up his power,
so if he does get past us

230
00:12:20,854 --> 00:12:24,558
the Blue King will be
waiting to stop him for

231
00:12:24,591 --> 00:12:26,760
sure. That's the plan.

232
00:12:27,193 --> 00:12:29,563
Hey, listen, don't get me
wrong, here. I have no

233
00:12:29,596 --> 00:12:31,264
problem with the
strategy itself.

234
00:12:32,098 --> 00:12:34,868
What I'm talking
about is his attitude

235
00:12:34,901 --> 00:12:37,337
and his sense of honor.

236
00:12:37,370 --> 00:12:40,206
I just don't understand
why anyone would

237
00:12:40,206 --> 00:12:41,875
want to follow that guy.

238
00:12:43,610 --> 00:12:45,045
Dishonest bastard...

239
00:12:48,048 --> 00:12:49,750
Dumbass! Don't make
such a fuss over

240
00:12:49,783 --> 00:12:51,217
other people's business!

241
00:12:52,118 --> 00:12:54,555
Sorry, Seri. Forgive him.

242
00:12:54,588 --> 00:12:58,258
Huh?! Oh, no, I, uh,
wasn't talking about you!

243
00:13:01,401 --> 00:13:02,235
Hey!

244
00:13:10,043 --> 00:13:11,645
Everyone, get back.

245
00:13:12,378 --> 00:13:13,580
What is it?

246
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,882
He's coming now.

247
00:13:33,399 --> 00:13:34,601
[chuckle]

248
00:13:47,848 --> 00:13:48,915
[groans]

249
00:13:53,286 --> 00:13:55,622
Agh! Shit! Didn't
see that coming!

250
00:13:56,122 --> 00:13:58,258
So that is the Green King?!

251
00:13:58,659 --> 00:13:59,793
Anna!

252
00:14:04,037 --> 00:14:05,205
Are you injured?!

253
00:14:06,339 --> 00:14:07,307
I'm fine.

254
00:14:07,974 --> 00:14:10,276
I'm going. I
have to stop him.

255
00:14:14,347 --> 00:14:15,215
Anna!

